13 NEW SECTION. Section 16. Definition. As used in [sections 16 through 19], "inpatient behavioral
14 health setting" means any setting, the primary purpose of which is to provide inpatient behavioral health care
15 consistent with eligible uses established in 50-1-119(3)(c).
