17 NEW SECTION. Section 17. Inpatient behavioral health setting infrastructure account -- use. (1)
18 There is an account within the state special revenue fund provided for in 17-2-102 called the inpatient
19 behavioral health setting infrastructure account to provide grant funding to nonprofit corporations that provide
20 inpatient behavioral health consistent with eligible uses established in 50-1-119 and for administrative costs
21 related to administering the grants. The department of public health and human services shall administer the
22 account.
23 (2) Up to 3% of the funds appropriated in [section 21] may be allocated for the department's
24 administrative costs.
